Memimi: Ah, not embarrassing at all! It was a breeze, I

Memimi: It was a mistake to see me as just any other girl!

Underling: It was a fitting resolution for someone worthy of
being an executive in our organization...! Ah, crap... When

Memimi: (Uooooooohhhhhhhhhhhhhhh...!!! So embarrassing...
Nooo, ah, ugh, uwaahhhhhhhh...! ...Ugh, uguuuuuh"...!)

Memimi: I'm so tired... How am I supposed to face people and
walk in public from tomorrow on... Uuuu... I've really done
it... Completely...

Unseen by anyone, Memimi continued to cry alone until
nightfall...
